--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.4.0 (2020-09-03)
C: Rename Ansible role from grafana to grafana_centos

* Version 0.3.0 (2019-10-21)
F: Add support for CentOS 8
E: Update configuration file to Grafana version 6

* Version 0.2.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 0.1.0 (2019-01-21)
F: Initial release
